1
00:00:00,080 --> 00:00:03,926
QualCanvas is a visual workspace for qualitative researchers.

2
00:00:03,926 --> 00:00:08,733
It keeps transcripts, codes, analytical connections and research memos together,

3
00:00:08,733 --> 00:00:13,540
so you can see how an interpretation developed instead of

4
00:00:13,540 --> 00:00:15,944
reconstructing it at the end.

5
00:00:16,344 --> 00:00:20,855
The product is designed for interview studies, field notes, open-text

6
00:00:20,855 --> 00:00:23,561
survey responses and other qualitative material.

7
00:00:23,561 --> 00:00:28,072
The first goal is simple: bring a source into a

8
00:00:28,072 --> 00:00:31,680
workspace without turning your analysis into a spreadsheet.

9
00:00:32,080 --> 00:00:35,175
On the canvas, each source remains readable.

10
00:00:35,175 --> 00:00:39,597
Codes sit beside the passages they describe, and the links

11
00:00:39,597 --> 00:00:43,576
between them make recurring patterns visible across the study.

12
00:00:43,976 --> 00:00:49,142
When you are ready to analyse, the tools are grouped by purpose.

13
00:00:49,142 --> 00:00:53,447
Explore text, inspect coding patterns, compare cases or build a

14
00:00:53,447 --> 00:00:57,752
framework matrix without losing the path back to the source.

15
00:00:58,152 --> 00:01:02,321
The codebook gives the project a shared vocabulary.

16
00:01:02,321 --> 00:01:07,533
Review definitions, counts and hierarchy, then refine the structure as

17
00:01:07,533 --> 00:01:09,096
your interpretation changes.

18
00:01:09,496 --> 00:01:14,133
Export a report for writing, an Excel workbook for review,

19
00:01:14,133 --> 00:01:18,771
an image for a presentation, or QDPX for exchange with

20
00:01:18,771 --> 00:01:20,162
compatible qualitative-analysis tools.

21
00:01:20,162 --> 00:01:23,872
Your work is not trapped in the canvas.

22
00:01:24,272 --> 00:01:28,062
Start with one transcript and one research question.

23
00:01:28,062 --> 00:01:32,801
Build the interpretation in small, reviewable steps, and use the

24
00:01:32,801 --> 00:01:36,117
guide whenever you need the next task.

25
00:01:36,117 --> 00:01:38,960
Visit qualcanvas dot com to begin.
